81538065-1918-4997-b309-468e30558649.title: Aggie
81538065-1918-4997-b309-468e30558649.text: What can I help you with?

options.text: What could you make for me?
Could you think of a way to make skin paste?
Cool, do you turn people into frogs?
You mad old witch, you can't help me.
Can you make dyes for me please?

76b8462a-7fc9-45b6-b51b-e38bdb375153.title: <player>
76b8462a-7fc9-45b6-b51b-e38bdb375153.text: What could you make for me?

9d2a35f3-14f5-4412-945f-27cb404719f7.title: Aggie
9d2a35f3-14f5-4412-945f-27cb404719f7.text:
I mostly just make what I find pretty. I sometimes
make dye for the women's clothes to brighten the place
up. I can make red, yellow and blue dyes. If you'd like
some, just bring me the appropriate ingredients.

options.text: What do you need to make red dye?
What do you need to make yellow dye?
What do you need to make blue dye?
No thanks, I am happy the colour I am.

bd288edc-a009-490f-b3fa-bcb602f15dd3.title: <player>
bd288edc-a009-490f-b3fa-bcb602f15dd3.text: What do you need to make red dye?

f9c60078-b8ed-44a4-91b3-33d3b7897570.title: Aggie
f9c60078-b8ed-44a4-91b3-33d3b7897570.text: 3 lots of redberries and 5 coins to you.

options.text: Okay, make me some red dye please.
I don't think I have all the ingredients yet.
I can do without dye at that price.
Where do I get redberries?
What other colours can you make?

f5657344-25b8-48e8-9c84-de993af5cda3.title: <player>
f5657344-25b8-48e8-9c84-de993af5cda3.text: Ok make me some red dye please.

b8a8a4a1-e68a-444b-ac95-4f0662c8a65d.text:
You hand the redberries and payment to Aggie. Aggie
produces a red bottle and hands it to you.

5d908959-0235-4b87-9418-eb8be4f09eb6.title: <player>
5d908959-0235-4b87-9418-eb8be4f09eb6.text: I don't think I have all the ingredients yet.

38975f95-d2d3-465e-b9cc-9e8043b22de1.title: Aggie
38975f95-d2d3-465e-b9cc-9e8043b22de1.text:
You know what you need to get, now come back when
you have them. Goodbye for now.

c66f6eaa-8407-437f-872a-8d5274b08df2.title: <player>
c66f6eaa-8407-437f-872a-8d5274b08df2.text: I can do without dye at that price.

17f1f8a5-fc51-481c-bdfa-c658f6fb99a1.title: Aggie
17f1f8a5-fc51-481c-bdfa-c658f6fb99a1.text:
That's your choice, but I would think you have killed
for less. I can see it in your eyes.

ecd8c541-7d15-4046-a2b2-6b6f75981488.title: Aggie
ecd8c541-7d15-4046-a2b2-6b6f75981488.text:
I pick mine from the woods south of Varrock. The food
shop in Port Sarim sometimes has some as well.

2f6c688e-db05-4379-8055-e45890360b30.title: <player>
2f6c688e-db05-4379-8055-e45890360b30.text: What other colours can you make?

fa564baf-7eb0-4f32-891d-5f42c132108c.title: Aggie
fa564baf-7eb0-4f32-891d-5f42c132108c.text: Red, yellow and blue. Which one would you like?

1208de18-9afb-4331-a65d-5e2612fba08c.title: <player>
1208de18-9afb-4331-a65d-5e2612fba08c.text: What do you need to make yellow dye?

70898a0d-2936-4603-9aaa-15ce8d248101.title: Aggie
70898a0d-2936-4603-9aaa-15ce8d248101.text:
Yellow is a strange colour to get, comes from onion
skins. I need 2 onions and 5 coins to make yellow dye.

options.text: Okay, make me some yellow dye please.
I don't think I have all the ingredients yet.
I can do without dye at that price.
Where do I get onions?
What other colours can you make?

301c7721-7685-4311-9fd0-eea9625faa8f.title: Aggie
301c7721-7685-4311-9fd0-eea9625faa8f.text:
There are some onions growing on a farm to the East
of here, next to the sheep field.

options.text: What other colours can you make?
Thanks.

e2e546aa-616e-4518-913b-25fc4f0a6483.title: <player>
e2e546aa-616e-4518-913b-25fc4f0a6483.text: Ok make me some yellow dye please.

9fd09c60-27c3-4ab3-a610-88ca20db3e83.text:
You hand the onions and payment to Aggie. Aggie
produces a yellow bottle and hands it to you.

f6bda0fb-66fd-40b4-896d-351374e12839.title: <player>
f6bda0fb-66fd-40b4-896d-351374e12839.text: What do you need to make blue dye?

79a59d48-be22-4788-a191-686ff93240ba.title: Aggie
79a59d48-be22-4788-a191-686ff93240ba.text: 2 woad leaves and 5 coins to you.

options.text: Okay, make me some blue dye please.
I don't think I have all the ingredients yet.
I can do without dye at that price.
Where do I get woad leaves?
What other colours can you make?

30996bf7-1cf9-4ed3-bd1d-c236ade76cc6.title: <player>
30996bf7-1cf9-4ed3-bd1d-c236ade76cc6.text: Where do I get woad leaves?

5d4f814a-7bff-410c-b682-6bd06b513fd5.title: Aggie
5d4f814a-7bff-410c-b682-6bd06b513fd5.text:
Woad leaves are fairly hard to find. My other
customers tell me the chief gardener in Falador grows
them.

8c355b72-423d-4d5b-b8b4-bf708ee3bc1f.title: <player>
8c355b72-423d-4d5b-b8b4-bf708ee3bc1f.text: Ok make me some blue dye please.

2ebb7e75-8ae3-493b-9cf7-29c3519cb951.text:
You hand the woad leaves and payment to Aggie. Aggie
produces a blue bottle and hands it to you.

c3858d3c-ae44-4518-8592-515b95dd325d.title: <player>
c3858d3c-ae44-4518-8592-515b95dd325d.text: No thanks, I am happy the colour I am.

51c6d247-d6f0-4b26-9a06-340c6277f12c.title: Aggie
51c6d247-d6f0-4b26-9a06-340c6277f12c.text:
You are easily pleased with yourself then.
When you need dyes, come to me.

e5c5c1e8-ae55-4420-be74-2f230c231e64.title: <player>
e5c5c1e8-ae55-4420-be74-2f230c231e64.text: Cool, do you turn people into frogs?

c6b0a9dc-6c73-4b5b-b679-afbd0209be38.title: Aggie
c6b0a9dc-6c73-4b5b-b679-afbd0209be38.text:
Oh, not for years, but if you meet a talking chicken,
you have probably met the professor in the manor north
of here. A few years ago it was flying fish. That
machine is a menace.

e5ca8500-297d-4ecc-84bb-7aca61cf7586.title: <player>
e5ca8500-297d-4ecc-84bb-7aca61cf7586.text: You mad old witch, you can't help me.

ffe5485c-963a-4814-b973-52b024866fbd.title: Aggie
ffe5485c-963a-4814-b973-52b024866fbd.text: Oh, you like to call a witch names do you?

a10f9dbb-5c8d-41a0-8b5c-6d9c167b29f0.text:
Aggie waves her hands about, and you seem to be 20
coins poorer.

3ad54fc3-7f97-48f9-9f7f-b62eb60c99a5.text:
Aggie waves her hands about, and you seem to be five
coins poorer.

1c56bb68-5da6-4a86-a55c-a16ccd9e2cb5.title: Aggie
1c56bb68-5da6-4a86-a55c-a16ccd9e2cb5.text:
Thank you for your kind present of some flour. I am
sure you never meant to insult me.

64ff886c-b7b3-4aee-99bd-5839217e96e8.title: Aggie
64ff886c-b7b3-4aee-99bd-5839217e96e8.text:
You should be careful about insulting a witch. You never
know what shape you could wake up in.

010281f7-25e2-48cc-9931-b40122bf9825.title: <player>
010281f7-25e2-48cc-9931-b40122bf9825.text: Can you make dyes for me please?

f262cd89-4842-49a7-8b50-d477d5d40e9f.title: Aggie
f262cd89-4842-49a7-8b50-d477d5d40e9f.text: What sort of dye would you like? Red, yellow or blue?

db6702a8-c41a-4ee9-b003-a643fe52587c.title: <player>
db6702a8-c41a-4ee9-b003-a643fe52587c.text: Could you think of a way to make skin paste?

830eb9a3-1f9d-4b59-b70d-0666bb60969f.title: Aggie
830eb9a3-1f9d-4b59-b70d-0666bb60969f.text:
Yes I can, I would need ash, flour, water and
redberries to make that.

0dd4da79-aef2-4cb0-82d1-4074cba71340.title: Aggie
0dd4da79-aef2-4cb0-82d1-4074cba71340.text:
Yes I can, I see you already have the ingredients.
Would you like me to mix some for you now?

options.text: Yes please. Mix me some skin paste.
No thank you, I don't need any skin paste right now.

75e9b20c-4387-4441-a493-cb987060a32a.title: <player>
75e9b20c-4387-4441-a493-cb987060a32a.text: No thank you, I don't need any skin paste right now.

8348afda-399b-4b60-837e-c9a434066036.title: Aggie
8348afda-399b-4b60-837e-c9a434066036.text: Okay dearie, that's always your choice.

96ec251e-2078-4cc8-be14-d059381d94b7.title: <player>
96ec251e-2078-4cc8-be14-d059381d94b7.text: Yes please. Mix me some skin paste.

cad77181-81fc-4f60-99c0-7fb8b8ecb3ef.title: Aggie
cad77181-81fc-4f60-99c0-7fb8b8ecb3ef.text: That should be simple. Hand the things to Aggie then.

65090ce2-ab41-46a8-9a5a-ccc7a33b12a0.text:
You hand the ash, flour, water and redberries to Aggie.
Aggie tips the ingredients into a cauldron
and mutters some words.

3250db88-643f-4014-8b42-9393229299f3.text: Aggie hands you the skin paste.

01d992bd-1aa2-45f9-a57b-11bd3a5607c5.title: Aggie
01d992bd-1aa2-45f9-a57b-11bd3a5607c5.text:
There you go dearie, your skin potion. That will make
you look good at the Varrock dances.
